# v0.3.11 (Pre-release)

## What's Changed

* Nvidia Cosmos 7B and 14B: text to video and image to video diffusion model support.
    <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-OCwHBur0FM" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>


* New sampler: res_multistep
* ckpt/pt/etc.. files are now always loaded safely on pytorch 2.4 and above.
* Fix some cases of ancestral samplers not being deterministic.
* Support ascend npu by @ji-huazhong [#5436](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/5436)
* Add option to log non-error output to stdout by @webfiltered [#6243](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6243)
* serve workflow templates from custom_nodes by @bezo97 [#6193](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6193)
* Remove duplicate calls to INPUT_TYPES by @catboxanon [#6249](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6249)
* Fix Hook Keyframe 'guarantee_steps' behavior and add 'sigmas' by @Kosinkadink [#6273](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6273)
* Add kl_optimal scheduler by @blepping [#6206](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6206)
* (fix): "verbose" argument by @bigcat88 [#6289](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6289)
* Fix custom node type-hinting examples by @webfiltered [#6281](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6281)
* Add missing model_options param to finalize_default_conds call by @Kosinkadink [#6296](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6296)
* Fix unknown scheduler error handling in calculate_sigmas function by @blepping [#6280](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6280)
* Fix temporal tiling for Tiled VAE decoder, remove redundant tiles. by @kvochko [#6306](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6306)
* Update web content to release v1.6.14 by @huchenlei [#6312](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6312)
* add fov and mask for load 3d node by @jtydhr88 [#6308](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6308)
* Update web content to release v1.6.15 by @huchenlei [#6324](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6324)
* Update web content to release v1.6.16 by @huchenlei [#6335](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6335)
* Update web content to release v1.6.17 by @huchenlei [#6337](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6337)
* Add update-frontend github action by @huchenlei [#6336](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6336)
* Update CODEOWNERS by @yoland68 [#6338](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6338)
* In inner_sample, change "sigmas" to "sample_sigmas" by @Kosinkadink [#6360](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6360)
* Frontend Update: v1.6.18 by @huchenlei [#6368](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6368)
* Document get_attr and get_model_object by @huchenlei [#6357](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6357)
* fixed: robust loading \`comfy.settings.json\` by @ltdrdata [#6383](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6383)
* Add pyproject.toml by @huchenlei [#6386](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6386)
* Hooks Part 2 - TransformerOptionsHook and AdditionalModelsHook by @Kosinkadink [#6377](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6377)
* Merge ruff.toml into pyproject.toml by @huchenlei [#6431](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6431)
* (fix): load_extra_path_config: relative path not converted to a full path by @bigcat88 [#6395](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6395)
* Rewrite res_multistep sampler and implement res_multistep_cfg_pp sampler by @pamparamm [#6462](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6462)
* Add SetFirstSigma node by @catboxanon [#6459](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/pull/6459)

**Full Changelog**: [\`v0.3.10...v0.3.11\`](https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI/compare/v0.3.10...v0.3.11)
